00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,770
Official Zang.

6
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,100
 At the beginning of every New Year, 

7
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:49,020
 the Emperor opens the Hall of Histories in the Palace, 

8
00:01:49,020 --> 00:01:51,510
 and the Cabinet recruits historians from the six departments 

9
00:01:51,510 --> 00:01:54,600
 to compile the history of the country, which lasts for a few days. 

10
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:57,660
As Vice Minister of Works and Imperial Astronomer,

11
00:01:57,660 --> 00:02:00,610
I will be one of the historians this time.

12
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:18,280
   

13
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:26,150
Are you going back?

14
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:29,630
The parts I was responsible for have all been compiled.

15
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:33,030
I've informed the cabinet that I'd be leaving tonight.

16
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,430
Today is the Lantern Festival,

17
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:36,530
so the Historian ordered the maids to make some glutinous rice balls

18
00:02:36,530 --> 00:02:37,740
and prepare some snacks.

19
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:40,370
I'd better keep my appetite until I reach home.

20
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:43,420
- Taste these glutinous rice balls for me. 
 - Thank you, sir.

21
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:45,210
Tonight, there will be fireworks outside the palace.

22
00:02:45,210 --> 00:02:47,600
You're just in time to see them.

23
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,210
 Even if you could sneak into the palace, 

24
00:02:57,210 --> 00:03:00,400
 could you get into the heavily guarded Hanzhang Hall? 

25
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,140
 At the Lantern Festival every year, 

26
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:04,560
 a feast is held in the palace. 

27
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:07,910
 That night, the Emperor will not be in Hanzhang Hall, 

28
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:11,190
 and fireworks will be set off all over the capital. 

29
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:15,880
 I need you to set off the greatest fireworks at the right time 

30
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:20,050
 so that the people of the capital will always remember this night. 

31
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,310
 When you stare at bright lights for too long, 

32
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:41,520
 you can't see the darkness. 

33
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:45,790
 The brighter the fireworks, the safer my path will be. 

